{"tid":1830861,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發要記者！】屏山北參選人羅庭輝就選舉不公提出選舉呈請！","createTime":"2020-01-20T03:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T07:47:50.000Z","uid":19145,"like":344,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"efe78fadddbe27f14a83b7136b527ce47351023c","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:05:06.000Z","msg":"【採訪邀請】<br />\n<br />\n正式就屏山北選舉不公提出選舉呈請<br />\n<br />\n素人羅庭輝挑戰鄉事建制，在元朗屏山北僅以兩票落敗，但在選舉過程中建制派候選人出現大量違規情況，包括威嚇選民和票站主任，導致票站主任監督選舉過程未能公正地履行職務。<br />\n<br />\n此外，選舉還有各區執法尺度不一的情況，選舉若未能公正，將嚴重影響賽果及合法性。因此羅庭輝提出呈請，一為屏山北居民爭取公義，二為日後鄉郊參選人爭取公平的選舉環境，並促使政府盡快修改法例，改善選舉制度及令選舉人員能履行職務，維護選舉公平<br />\n<br />\n地點：高院門口<br />\n時間：1月20日(一) 2:45pm-3:30pm<br />\n<br />\n出席：<br />\n元朗屏山北參選人 羅庭輝<br />\n北區區議會主席 羅庭德<br />\n多區素人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yD4QtBH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyD4QtBH.png&h=4a8fd35a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北區區議會主席：警隊無惡不作應重組，本土派終極目標奪政權<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814557\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814557</a>"},{"pid":"7d8171b292544cca16aa2ad549936ad81cd010b8","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「警察僭竊擅權，無惡不作，只有重組警隊，重申制憲，方能為人民充權」。<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9c6508199b7b6b85ea48501f32060a7b4bada0d3","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"十連1/10"},{"pid":"1a2f4c574ee898ad31d57ff3ed7fd977b0baca39","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"十連2/10"},{"pid":"12ae05ef9a6f91ac4165fd382d9a02c404301a53","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:07:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「我們的終極目標是入主禮賓府，成為添馬政權的執政聯盟，奪取政權，實現煲底之約，與港人普天同慶，以祭義士亡魂」</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a9cff4a31e2695deea89f71b3caf4150d640ee6e","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「實現煲底之約，與港人普天同慶，以祭義士亡魂」</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6aa7730ecef37ae52b952eab07a4ada0e9bb1768","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:07:53.000Z","msg":"召喚記者！！"},{"pid":"075d9fc6a86a9fd9da946e41ad21d0455756794a","tid":1830861,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"e008b7cc797e67363e181c2076c5186040bf9d2d","tid":1830861,"uid":87891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:08:26.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"0c04cbb8cd492ec131e4c96e858171f2c47e2735","tid":1830861,"uid":207614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:10:37.000Z","msg":"記者!"},{"pid":"3cca24379339a88d78036452b94f34af22b71ebf","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:34:29.000Z","msg":"要記者！！！"},{"pid":"98ab553ae47e9e91afabae4110d61568689aa5ca","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:34:39.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬記者朋友！"},{"pid":"4c5b8a762353729fa88f96ec994fc1d8c4bc1ded","tid":1830861,"uid":19145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:46:03.000Z","msg":"記者朋友！！"},{"pid":"284f63b635a2fc7875db3fb592a0d1493a341883","tid":1830861,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:48:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17fc36b8d56bbad910a0e09538d77f7034a3ac23","tid":1830861,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T03:48:55.000Z","msg":"要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whiteho